long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Introducing the Literal to Readwise Sync extension for Chrome - the bridge between your completed books on Literal and your Readwise account. Dive deep into your reading insights without missing a beat. 

While Literal helps you share and insipre your friends with your discoveries, the sync will help you with revisiting those in Readwise and frequently get inspired again!

This chrome extenstion retrieves data from Literal (https://literal.club), using Literal's API and sends the data to Readwise's API (https://readwise.io) using your private token (not password).

This extension is a third-party creation and is not affiliated with Literal or Readwise.
